# Event System Conventions

- Use `agrogame.events.EventBus` and `BaseEvent` across modules
- Emit events with minimal payload; `BaseEvent.to_dict()` supports logging/visualization
- Handlers must be fast and side-effect scoped; avoid cross-module state mutation
- Prefer module-local events; keep contracts stable and documented
- Debug logging of all events is enabled at emit; leverage for troubleshooting

